WEBVTT

00:00:19.250 --> 00:00:24.359
ظآزThe whole world is lit upظآز

00:00:24.360 --> 00:00:25.979
ظآزBecause you existظآز

00:00:25.980 --> 00:00:28.019
ظآزYou're alwaysظآز

00:00:28.020 --> 00:00:32.679
ظآزSomewhere close, flying with meظآز

00:00:32.680 --> 00:00:35.299
ظآزGo to where the wind blowsظآز

00:00:35.300 --> 00:00:37.019
ظآزHold tightظآز

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:42.879
ظآزTo the ray of light that belongs to usظآز

00:00:42.880 --> 00:00:48.200
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 2=

00:01:06.970 --> 00:01:08.090
Don't make a sound.

00:01:19.970 --> 00:01:21.090
It's you.

00:01:26.210 --> 00:01:27.539
I left in such a hurry that day.

00:01:27.540 --> 00:01:28.620
I owe you a thank you.

00:01:28.740 --> 00:01:29.810
Thank you for saving me.

00:01:30.020 --> 00:01:30.939
It was my duty.

00:01:30.940 --> 00:01:32.420
There's no need for thanks, Miss Mu.

00:01:42.850 --> 00:01:44.370
Then, why are you following me?

00:01:44.580 --> 00:01:46.220
Since you've already recognized me,

00:01:46.580 --> 00:01:48.220
allow me to introduce myself.

00:01:48.300 --> 00:01:49.379
My name is Shen Jibai.

00:01:49.380 --> 00:01:51.420
I'm the new
Head of Security for Mu Group.

00:01:55.850 --> 00:01:57.209
I know who you are.

00:01:57.210 --> 00:01:58.659
(Personal Info: Shen Jibai)
Shen Jibai

00:01:58.660 --> 00:02:00.659
is the new
Head of Security for Mu Group.

00:02:00.660 --> 00:02:01.730
There are also rumors

00:02:01.900 --> 00:02:02.969
saying

00:02:02.970 --> 00:02:05.060
that he's your stepmom's secret lover.

00:02:06.100 --> 00:02:07.620
A secret lover?

00:02:08.460 --> 00:02:09.529
But

00:02:09.530 --> 00:02:11.419
I don't think I need
your protection right now,

00:02:11.420 --> 00:02:12.300
Captain Shen.

00:02:15.140 --> 00:02:17.580
Miss Mu, you're being
a bit too full of yourself.

00:02:17.770 --> 00:02:19.460
I'm under Ms. Xu's orders

00:02:19.700 --> 00:02:21.300
to protect this painting.

00:02:21.740 --> 00:02:23.019
Otherwise, according to protocol,

00:02:23.020 --> 00:02:25.530
how could
this painting be in your hands?

00:02:26.490 --> 00:02:27.850
Fair enough.

00:02:27.980 --> 00:02:28.649
I

00:02:28.650 --> 00:02:30.459
am just an auctioneer.

00:02:30.460 --> 00:02:31.859
I'm neither a financial backer

00:02:31.860 --> 00:02:33.650
nor a secret lover.

00:02:33.900 --> 00:02:35.250
Of course, I don't need protection.

00:02:38.400 --> 00:02:41.680
(Elevator Lobby 3, Level B2)

00:03:40.420 --> 00:03:41.280
What happened?

00:03:41.280 --> 00:03:43.019
Why are you just standing there?
Go after them!

00:03:43.020 --> 00:03:44.000
- Yes, ma'am!
- Yes, ma'am!

00:03:49.490 --> 00:03:51.060
How did the painting end up like this?

00:03:54.300 --> 00:03:56.580
Such a good painting,
ruined just like that.

00:03:58.020 --> 00:03:59.809
If I had caught it just now, maybe...

00:03:59.810 --> 00:04:02.090
If you had caught it just now,
your hand would've been gone.

00:04:07.420 --> 00:04:08.900
It's just a painting.

00:04:09.020 --> 00:04:10.370
It's not worth more than a life.

00:04:11.740 --> 00:04:13.739
Since you're so nonchalant
about it, Captain Shen,

00:04:13.740 --> 00:04:14.899
then the rest of this

00:04:14.900 --> 00:04:17.460
will be handled by you,
the new Head of Security.

00:04:22.330 --> 00:04:23.900
(A bunch of idiots.)

00:04:24.210 --> 00:04:26.020
(Couldn't even handle a simple task.)

00:04:27.520 --> 00:04:31.760
(Mu's Villa)

00:04:42.460 --> 00:04:44.170
I wonder why, at this late hour,

00:04:44.210 --> 00:04:46.380
you're still at my house, Captain Shen.

00:04:46.730 --> 00:04:48.850
Is it because this afternoon's
matter has been cleared up?

00:04:49.140 --> 00:04:50.329
Jibai is someone

00:04:50.330 --> 00:04:52.780
I hired from abroad at a high salary
to be our Head of Security.

00:04:53.260 --> 00:04:55.139
You saw what happened today.

00:04:55.140 --> 00:04:57.850
I'm afraid it's not safe for
a mom and daughter like us at home.

00:04:58.020 --> 00:04:59.260
I've already decided.

00:04:59.330 --> 00:05:01.850
I'll have Jibai and his men
move in to protect us.

00:05:02.290 --> 00:05:04.020
Otherwise, if anything happens to you,

00:05:04.170 --> 00:05:06.260
I won't be able to answer to your dad.

00:05:06.900 --> 00:05:08.050
Is that so?

00:05:10.090 --> 00:05:12.220
Then, I'll have
to trouble you, Captain Shen.

00:05:15.330 --> 00:05:16.780
Since you mentioned my dad,

00:05:17.060 --> 00:05:18.730
how is he doing now?

00:05:18.940 --> 00:05:20.260
I want to go see him.

00:05:20.620 --> 00:05:22.780
Your dad is currently
recuperating in the hospital.

00:05:22.850 --> 00:05:25.220
He doesn't want anyone to disturb him.

00:05:26.900 --> 00:05:27.850
Really?

00:05:29.700 --> 00:05:31.169
I'm tired today.

00:05:31.170 --> 00:05:32.220
I'm going to rest.

00:05:40.850 --> 00:05:42.780
She's taking advantage
of my father's illness

00:05:43.060 --> 00:05:44.819
to sneak in and target the group.

00:05:44.820 --> 00:05:48.700
ظآزWading through
the muddy waters of hearts and timesظآز

00:05:49.290 --> 00:05:51.220
(As long as I am here,)

00:05:51.730 --> 00:05:53.410
(don't even think about succeeding.)

00:05:57.970 --> 00:06:02.109
ظآزWaking up between our dreamsظآز

00:06:02.110 --> 00:06:03.949
ظآزDrawing a circle of falling blossomsظآز

00:06:03.950 --> 00:06:06.520
ظآزTo record your book of poetryظآز

00:06:06.530 --> 00:06:08.580
(This pendant left by my mother,)

00:06:09.020 --> 00:06:11.340
(Mu Zhiyu has one exactly like it.)

00:06:11.850 --> 00:06:14.260
(What exactly
is the connection to the Mu family?)

00:06:14.770 --> 00:06:17.220
(I must uncover
the secret of the jade pendant)

00:06:17.260 --> 00:06:19.340
(and find out
the cause of my mother's death.)

00:06:20.010 --> 00:06:22.540
ظآزJust one devoted glanceظآز

00:06:22.620 --> 00:06:24.580
(Grandpa left this jade pendant to me,)

00:06:25.060 --> 00:06:27.260
(saying it's related to Mu Group.)

00:06:28.330 --> 00:06:30.200
(Now that Dad
is recuperating in the hospital)

00:06:30.290 --> 00:06:32.020
(and Stepmom won't let me see him,)

00:06:33.060 --> 00:06:34.380
(for the sake of Mu Group,)

00:06:34.850 --> 00:06:36.970
(I must hurry
and find clues about my dad.)

00:06:48.580 --> 00:06:49.699
Before entering my room,

00:06:49.700 --> 00:06:51.490
please knock first.

00:06:52.770 --> 00:06:55.329
Are you adjusting well
to this place, Captain Shen?

00:06:55.330 --> 00:06:56.579
Any instruction, Ms. Xu?

00:06:56.580 --> 00:06:58.969
Don't be fooled by Mu Zhiyu's
"rich heiress" act.

00:06:58.970 --> 00:07:01.050
While she's had
some success in her career,

00:07:01.140 --> 00:07:03.580
her romantic life is a complete blank.

00:07:03.620 --> 00:07:04.409
Next,

00:07:04.410 --> 00:07:05.209
it's up to you.

00:07:05.210 --> 00:07:06.170
Ms. Xu,

00:07:06.210 --> 00:07:07.729
this is different from

00:07:07.730 --> 00:07:08.900
our previous agreement.

00:07:09.290 --> 00:07:11.140
Currently, besides you,

00:07:11.380 --> 00:07:13.220
there is no better candidate.

00:07:13.820 --> 00:07:14.769
Don't forget,

00:07:14.770 --> 00:07:17.380
you only get the money
once the mission is complete.

00:07:18.620 --> 00:07:22.140
(Xu Mingzhu, if it weren't for
investigating my mother's death,)

00:07:22.700 --> 00:07:24.780
(how could I let you order me around?)

00:07:25.060 --> 00:07:27.170
(What a foolish woman.)

00:07:35.850 --> 00:07:38.619
(Since Xu Mingzhu refuses to reveal
the nursing home where my dad is,)

00:07:38.620 --> 00:07:40.820
(maybe there will be
some clues in the study.)

00:07:55.060 --> 00:07:57.969
Miss Mu, it's so late and you're not sleeping.

00:07:57.970 --> 00:07:59.220
What are you looking for here?

00:08:04.770 --> 00:08:06.459
I'm just walking around my own home.

00:08:06.460 --> 00:08:07.780
That's not a crime, is it?

00:08:08.530 --> 00:08:09.579
On the contrary,

00:08:09.580 --> 00:08:11.780
what are you doing here so late
instead of sleeping?

00:08:11.970 --> 00:08:12.900
I...

00:08:47.300 --> 00:08:50.650
ظآزIf my heart refuses
to compromise with the nightظآز

00:08:50.900 --> 00:08:54.179
ظآزI'll tear out my ribs
to strike the stars louderظآز

00:08:54.180 --> 00:08:57.450
ظآزSettling in my veinsظآز

00:08:58.400 --> 00:09:02.649
ظآزEvery flutterظآز

00:09:02.650 --> 00:09:03.730
Miss Mu,

00:09:04.290 --> 00:09:06.420
are you holding something in your hand?

00:09:06.960 --> 00:09:09.030
ظآزIf longing can be foldedظآز

00:09:09.500 --> 00:09:11.970
It's none of your business
what I take in my own home.

00:09:13.690 --> 00:09:16.300
You haven't answered
my question yet, Captain Shen.

00:09:16.810 --> 00:09:18.060
It's so late.

00:09:18.530 --> 00:09:19.770
What are you doing here?

00:09:21.730 --> 00:09:22.979
When I was patrolling tonight,

00:09:22.980 --> 00:09:25.060
I happened to see
someone acting suspiciously here.

00:09:25.220 --> 00:09:26.660
As the Head of Security,

00:09:26.740 --> 00:09:28.560
it's only right for me
to conduct a routine check.

00:09:28.560 --> 00:09:29.490
Isn't it?

00:09:32.290 --> 00:09:33.850
You mean that?

00:09:37.450 --> 00:09:39.529
I advise you, Captain Shen,

00:09:39.530 --> 00:09:41.970
to pay more attention to yourself.

00:09:52.100 --> 00:09:53.220
Hey.

00:09:53.770 --> 00:09:55.220
He's awake?

00:10:05.860 --> 00:10:06.940
Miss Mu,

00:10:08.100 --> 00:10:09.460
I still have to remind you.

00:10:10.450 --> 00:10:11.409
Don't wander around

00:10:11.410 --> 00:10:13.460
at night in the future,

00:10:14.020 --> 00:10:16.370
lest you encounter
another accident like today.

00:10:17.900 --> 00:10:19.730
You should worry about yourself instead.

00:10:19.810 --> 00:10:21.409
Xu Mingzhu's harem
is full of talented men.

00:10:21.410 --> 00:10:23.859
Watch out, or you might
lose your position, Captain Shen.

00:10:23.860 --> 00:10:26.979
Miss Mu, with such a rich imagination,
why don't you become a screenwriter?

00:10:26.980 --> 00:10:28.169
Captain Shen,

00:10:28.170 --> 00:10:29.339
being so paranoid,

00:10:29.340 --> 00:10:30.730
why don't you become a detective?

00:10:45.020 --> 00:10:46.049
(This logo,)

00:10:46.050 --> 00:10:47.890
(I need He Min to check on it.)

00:10:48.340 --> 00:10:51.060
(Maybe I can find my dad.)

00:10:52.760 --> 00:10:56.760
(Mu Group)

00:10:58.220 --> 00:10:59.769
(This Xu Mingzhu truly knows)

00:10:59.770 --> 00:11:01.370
(nothing about auctions.)

00:11:02.380 --> 00:11:04.490
(If Mu Group
continues to be run like this,)

00:11:04.570 --> 00:11:06.400
(it will all be
squandered sooner or later.)

00:11:15.050 --> 00:11:16.899
Captain Shen, if you have nothing else to do,

00:11:16.900 --> 00:11:18.010
you can leave now.

00:11:18.520 --> 00:11:21.499
I'm afraid that if I leave, you will encounter
danger again in a moment, Miss Mu.

00:11:21.500 --> 00:11:24.250
I wonder if my bazi
just clashes with yours.

00:11:24.340 --> 00:11:26.300
I run into all sorts of accidents
whenever I see you.

00:11:26.810 --> 00:11:28.010
It seems

00:11:28.690 --> 00:11:29.970
helping you was unnecessary.

00:11:36.860 --> 00:11:37.580
Hello?

00:11:37.770 --> 00:11:38.379
Hello,

00:11:38.380 --> 00:11:39.130
Yu.

00:11:39.450 --> 00:11:40.820
Is it convenient to talk?

00:11:41.140 --> 00:11:43.250
There's a lead on that logo
you asked me to check.

00:11:43.650 --> 00:11:44.890
There's a cocktail party tonight.

00:11:44.900 --> 00:11:45.970
Let's meet and talk.

00:11:45.980 --> 00:11:47.940
No problem.
I'll definitely be there on time.

00:11:48.360 --> 00:11:49.180
Okay.

00:11:49.220 --> 00:11:50.090
See you tonight.

00:12:01.980 --> 00:12:03.259
I'm going home to change.

00:12:03.260 --> 00:12:04.490
Are you going to follow me too?

00:12:04.620 --> 00:12:05.259
Of course.

00:12:05.260 --> 00:12:06.460
From now on,

00:12:06.530 --> 00:12:08.569
I will protect
your safety 24 hours a day.

00:12:08.570 --> 00:12:10.250
I won't let
another accident happen to you.

00:12:12.140 --> 00:12:13.139
Fine, then.

00:12:13.140 --> 00:12:14.180
Let's go.

00:12:19.740 --> 00:12:22.250
Don't be fooled by Mu Zhiyu's
"rich heiress" act.

00:12:23.170 --> 00:12:25.730
Her romantic life is a complete blank.

00:12:26.860 --> 00:12:27.890
Next,

00:12:28.020 --> 00:12:29.090
it's up to you.

